name: Honda Civic 2021
description: The Honda Civic is a good compact car that offers fun driving dynamics without sacrificing ride comfort. Additionally, it delivers quick acceleration and great fuel economy, regardless of which engine you choose. The Civic is available as a sedan and a hatchback for 2021, and both body styles provide plenty of passenger space and cargo room..
